items.badge_description: What happens when you take two or more amazing breweries, throw them into the tank and let them ferment together? An amazing collaboration beer, that’s what! Cheers to working together to create the perfect flavor. That's 15 different beers that have been brewed as a collaboration. Try 5 more for Level 4!

Right about now you’re feeling your face tighten and your taste buds explode. The full pucker is quickly setting in and you can’t get enough. This is the wonder of the sour. That's 40 different Sour Beers. Try 5 more for Level 9.

It’s been a long day and now it’s time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 10 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer or Sour - Fruited. Try 5 more for Level 3.
